  "texts": [
    "AlphaFold 3, an AI model developed by Isomorphic Labs and Google DeepMind, predicts the structure and interactions of proteins, RNA, DNA, and ligands with the aim of revolutionizing drug development and biological knowledge.",
    "Insilico Medicine's Pharma.AI is a generative AI platform that uses RNNs and custom algorithms for disease target discovery, drug design, and clinical trial prediction.Creating 3D models for prototyping and virtual reality experiences Analyzing complex scientific datasets Scientific summaries Molecular design optimization and drug discovery [15,28,35,36] 54.2%, improving over ChatGPT-3.5 (45%), while Google Bard significantly outperformed both with 100% accuracy, highlighting the varying capabilities of these tools in processing and applying orthopedic knowledge.",
    "Lubitz et al.",
    "assessed ChatGPT and Google Bard on the Orthopedic In-Training Examination (OITE), with ChatGPT scoring 69.1%, improving to 77.8% when provided with text descriptions of image based questions [52].",
    "Google Bard scored 49.8%, versus 58% with the text descriptions, emphasizing the current limitation of generative AI in interpreting visual content and their reliance on textual descriptions to perform more effectively."
  ]
